      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNSET PARIS (4) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at this track over 488m behind Frogs Monelli (28.18) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings five times from 10 starts. Has ability and can bounce back. UNEQUALLED (7) has been a little hard to follow, missing the frame last time but was a Grade 6 winner three starts ago and has drawn 7 where he has two wins. Well placed here and should do much better. ASTON BRADLEY (1) found traffic in the run and collided, missing the frame when a 12 length sixth (28.20) at this track in a Grade 5. Should be in this for a long way. GOUDA MONELLI (2) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to make amends.",
